<section class="hero-shop">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>
      Shop Rasa 
    </h1>
    <p class="lead">
      There's a reason people keep calling Rasa "The Best Coffee Alternative Out There." We've brought together 12 all-star herbs that are all really, really, really good for you. 7 adaptogens, 2 shrooms, 50% prebiotics...all from Ayurveda, Chinese medicine, and Western herbalism. Rasa is a dark, roasty, flavorful, nutritious brew with a hint of cinnamon that you can savor all day long because it is caffeine free.
